revision.text: The '''Amulet Coin''' is an [[Oak Items|Oak Item]]. When equipped, it increases the amount of money gained. It notably does not affect {{pdollar}} earnings in dungeons, but affects earnings in most other situations. The Amulet Coin is unlocked after catching 30 unique Pokémon.

revision.text:
The '''Amulet Coin''' is an [[Oak Items|Oak Item]]. When equipped, it increases the amount of money gained. Note: does not affect {{pdollar}} earnings in dungeons.
Note, the description of the item mentions only battling, however the effect is applied whenever the player gains money. The Amulet Coin is unlocked after catching 30 unique Pokémon.
revision.comment: Importing a new version from external source
